  "description": "Canadian cannabis-industry entrepreneur (co-founder of Tweed/Canopy Growth) who in 2021 attempted to acquire MindGeek through Bruinen Investments — a vehicle assembled with former-RCMP advisors and Crime Stoppers International personnel — under the rubric of an audit-led 'ethical turnaround.' The bid (Project Narsil) failed; Ethical Capital Partners completed an acquisition in March 2023 along structurally similar lines.",
